OL,3,CMother withdraws son from school
OL,4,Ctransport over fears for his safety
OL,6,FA mother from St Austell has withdrawn
OL,7,Fher son, who has complex additional
OL,8,Fneeds, from school transport over
OL,9,Ffears for his safety.
OL,11,FKylie claims that Cornwall Council
OL,12,Ffailed to give the transport provider
OL,13,Fessential information regarding her
OL,14,Fson's health needs.
OL,16,FBut Cornwall Council has said it is
OL,17,Fcontinuing to work with the family to
OL,18,Ftry to resolve the situation to their
OL,19,Fsatisfaction.
