OL,3,CMother withdraws son from school
OL,4,Ctransport over fears for his safety
OL,6,FEight-year-old Logan has an autism
OL,7,Fdiagnosis which requires special care
OL,8,Fto manage his behaviour and keep him
OL,9,Fsafe.
OL,11,FHis mother said that Cornwall Council
OL,12,Fprovided him with a re-purposed,
OL,13,Ffrayed harness without any
OL,14,Finstructions or means of freeing it in
OL,15,Fan emergency.
OL,17,FKylie first raised her concerns with
OL,18,Fthe council nine months ago and they
OL,19,Fwere acknowledged.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
