OL,3,CMother withdraws son from school
OL,4,Ctransport over fears for his safety
OL,6,FHowever, when a new provider took over
OL,7,Fthe contract this year, she found they
OL,8,Falso had not been given crucial
OL,9,Finformation about Logan, so she
OL,10,Fwithdrew him from the transport.
OL,12,FShe said: "My son's provider was only
OL,13,Fgiven his name, his address, his date
OL,14,Fof birth and the time of his pick-up."
OL,16,FAccording to Kylie, this not only
OL,17,Fplaces Logan at risk, but also his
OL,18,Fdriver and members of the public.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
