OL,4,Ctransport over fears for his safety
OL,6,FShe explained: "His epilepsy - what
OL,7,Fwould happen in the event he had a
OL,8,Fseizure wearing that harness? Or what
OL,9,Fif another child on that transport had
OL,10,Fa medical emergency?
OL,12,F"If there's one PA to six or seven
OL,13,Fchildren, how do you prioritise which
OL,14,Fchild's needs go first?"
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
