OL,6,FIn a statement, Cornwall Council said:
OL,7,F"We do appreciate that any change to
OL,8,Ftransport arrangements can be
OL,9,Fdifficult, particularly for children
OL,10,Fwith complex needs, and are committed
OL,11,Fto working with all families and
OL,12,Ftransport providers to ensure any
OL,13,Finitial challenges can be overcome."
OL,15,FTransport for children with special
OL,16,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,17,F(SEND) remains a significant challenge
OL,18,Ffor local authorities in the country,
OL,19,Fwith increasing costs and demand.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
