OL,6,FBy law, councils must provide
OL,7,Ftransport to SEND pupils if they live
OL,8,Fmore than a set distance from their
OL,9,Fnearest suitable school.
OL,11,FIn England, the number of these pupils
OL,12,Fhas risen by a quarter since 2019,
OL,13,Fwith 31,000 using taxis, according to
OL,14,Fthe County Councils Network.
OL,16,FIn Cornwall, Kylie's case does not
OL,17,Fappear to be an isolated one.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
