OL,6,FIn December 2023, the Local Government
OL,7,FOmbudsman found that Cornwall Council
OL,8,Fcaused avoidable uncertainty and
OL,9,Fdistress to another parent over school
OL,10,Ftransport.
OL,12,FIt found the council at fault for its
OL,13,Fcommunication and for avoidable delay
OL,14,Fin trying to secure new transport
OL,15,Farrangements.
OL,17,FDespite this, it was found not at
OL,18,Ffault for failing to risk assess the
OL,19,Fchild's transport arrangements or its
OL,20,Fapproach to training.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
